name: Name Change
title: Name Change Assistance
description: Comprehensive support for legally changing your name, including affidavit preparation and gazette publication.

cards.title: Process Steps
items: 2. Newspaper Publication (One English, One Local Language)

cards.title: Process Duration
cards.content: Typically takes 2-4 weeks after Gazette application submission.

faqs.q: Is the Gazette publication mandatory?
faqs.a: Yes, for government purposes and passports, Gazette notification is often required.

faqs.q: Can I change my name for any reason?
faqs.a: Generally yes, provided it's not for fraudulent purposes or to hide identity from law enforcement.
